OBB Recruiting PodEpisode #1Show NotesAfter all the talk and preparation, Geo is here with the first installment of the OBB Recruiting Pod! In this episode, Geo touches on Elite Prospect Day, Battle Miami and lots of 2023 and 2024prospect talk. Geo also gives you the latest on final official visits before National Signing Day.
